# Colors
color background          color7  color235
color listnormal          color11   color235
color listnormal_unread   color2     color235
color listfocus           color7  color237
color listfocus_unread    color2  color237
color info                color4     color235
color article             color7   color235

# unbind keys
unbind-key ENTER
unbind-key j
unbind-key k
unbind-key J
unbind-key K

# bind keys - vim style
bind-key j down
bind-key k up
bind-key l open
bind-key h quit

# highlights
